result.execSummary:
The defendant Matthew W Tuggle was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Matthew W Tuggle is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Matthew W Tuggle was found guilty of Theft-Movable Property <=$2500 [Modifiers: PTAC], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 943.20(1)(a).
